data.description: Welcome to this 2019-built gem nestled in a Salazar cul-de-sac. With three bedrooms and two baths, it offers modern living at its finest. The open-concept interior is perfect for relaxing or entertaining. The well-appointed kitchen and primary bedroom with en-suite add luxury. Step into the backyard, complete with a fire pit for cozy evenings and a closed dog run for your furry friends. This sought-after location is close to amenities, parks, and schools, with Albuquerque's vibrant scene just a short drive away. Sellers also include $4,000 of sellers' credit with an acceptable offer.  Don't miss out!
